OL,3,COver 100,000 people left without power
OL,4,Cin France heatwave
OL,6,FOver 100,000 people in northwestern
OL,7,FFrance have been left without power as
OL,8,Fextremely high temperatures strained
OL,9,Fthe country's infrastructure,
OL,10,Faccording to local media reports.
OL,12,FThe outage took place in the commune
OL,13,Fof Ergue-Gaberic in Britanny on
OL,14,FTuesday evening, leaving a total of
OL,15,F68,000 households without electricity,
OL,16,Fofficials said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
