PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782393517
OL,3,COver 100,000 people left without power
OL,4,Cin France heatwave
OL,6,FFrench grid operators RTE and Enedis
OL,7,Fhave been working to fix the issue,
OL,8,Fbut power is not expected to be
OL,9,Frestored until the end of the day at
OL,10,Fthe earliest, local media reported.
OL,12,FThe outage, which involved a
OL,13,Ftransformer on the electricity grid
OL,14,Fand did not injure anyone, has still
OL,15,Fleft people sweltering in record-
OL,16,Fbreaking heat, which is sweeping
OL,17,Facross the whole country and broader
OL,18,FEurope.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
