OL,3,COver 100,000 people left without power
OL,4,Cin France heatwave
OL,6,FOfficials in southeastern France also
OL,7,Fsaid the heatwave was the most likely
OL,8,Freason for the additional deaths of
OL,9,Ftwo children, aged two and four, who
OL,10,Fwere found unconscious in a car
OL,11,Foutside their home in Carpentras in
OL,12,Fthe south east.
OL,14,FSales of fans and air conditioners
OL,15,Fhave also skyrocketed, with
OL,16,Fsupermarket Carrefour reporting it had
OL,17,Fsold a thousand times more units on
OL,18,FTuesday than on a normal day,
OL,19,Faccording to AFP.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
